Package org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.snowball

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SampledEdge
    Representation of a snowball sampled edge.
    SampledGraph
    Representation of a snowball sampled graph.
    SampledVertex
    Representation of a snowball sampled vertex.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SampledEdgeDecorator<E extends Edge>
    A decorated class that implements SampledEdge.
    SampledGraphProjection<G extends Graph,V extends Vertex,E extends Edge>
    Representation of a snowball sampled graph that wraps the original graph and uses it as delegate.
    SampledGraphProjectionBuilder<G extends Graph,V extends Vertex,E extends Edge>
    An GraphBuilder implementation to build sampled graph projections.
    SampledGraphProjectionFactory<G extends Graph,V extends Vertex,E extends Edge>
    A sampled graph projection factory is responsible for instantiating new sampled graph projections, vertex decorators and edge decorators.
    SampledVertexDecorator<V extends Vertex>
    A decorated class that implements SampeldVertex.
    SnowballAttributes
    Container class to store snowball related attributes.
